title: Denise's angry showdown with Keegan has big consequences in EastEnders | Metro News
text:
Duncan Lindsay for Metro.co.uk Saturday 11 Feb 2017 11:58 pm (Picture: BBC) 
It’s fair to say that Keegan is one of EastEnders’ most troublesome newcomers in a while and when he and Denise Fox end up having a very public showdown, events look set to spiral out of control, with dramatic consequences. 
While Denise is under a lot of strain as the adoption process continues, Kim continues to pester her for information on the baby’s progress and things start to get on top of a tense Denise. 
After opening up to Kim about her feelings, she ends up confronting Keegan when he makes disrespectful remarks. 
As Keegan squares up to Denise, she stands firm but the clash looks set to have a dramatic outcome as Denise takes actions that could bring her even more trouble. 
How far has Keegan pushed her and will Denise do something that she regrets? 
One to watch: Monday 20th February on BBC One at 8pm.
